text: Kevin Korozmán (born 2 March 1997) is a Hungarian footballer who plays as forward for Soroksár SC in Nemzeti Bajnokság II. == References == Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Nemzeti Bajnokság I players Category:Nemzeti Bajnokság II players Category:Ferencvárosi TC footballers Category:MTK Budapest FC players Category:Soroksár SC players
